      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·臣工之什·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有瞽.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有瞽有瞽，在周之庭。設業設虡，崇牙樹羽。應田縣鼓，鞉磬柷圉。
既備乃奏，簫管備舉。喤喤厥聲，肅雝和鳴，先祖是聽。
我客戾止，永觀厥成。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There are the blind musicians; there are the blind musicians;
In the court of (the temple of) Kâu.</seg>
      </tuv>
